rComments: Great prof! His lectures are very enjoyable; he makes them entertaining and almost casual. Teaches the material very well and clearly, tests are fair and I like the freedom of choice he gives for the paper. Don't need to worry about the readings as long as you know the important points of them, which he will discuss in class.

David Falardeau is an amazing professor. He is really kind and truly cares about everyone's success. He gives you a guideline of what to study for the exams which makes his midterm and final very easy if you read the material. Overall, I would take this professor again in a heartbeat because he is engaging and his exams are easy.
